FBIS4-59906 "drnes097_a_94003" FBIS-NES-94-097 Daily Report 19 May 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Zeroual Issues Pardon for `About 1,000' Prisoners Zeroual Issues Pardon for `About 1,000' Prisoners LD1905102194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1000 GMT 19 May 94 LD1905102194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Text] President of the Republic Liamine Zeroual has issued a legal decree based on the recommendation of the justice minister stipulating the pardon of prisoners who were involved in cases not related to crimes of terrorism, sabotage, and state security. The decree stipulates the cancellation of the prison sentences for those who were sentenced to three months' imprisonment, which allows the release of about 1,000 prisners. It also stipulates the partial reduction of prison sentences ranging between 4 and 7 months.
